<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Decline Email</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com"> 
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Raleway:ital,wght@0,100..900;1,100..900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: "Raleway", sans-serif;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .wrapper {
            width: 800px;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            position: relative;
            overflow: visible;
            margin: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        
        .Name {
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
           
        }
        .subject {
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
           color: #384860;
        }
        .header {
            width: 100%;
            height: 104px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 42.46px 48px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        .zoracom-logo {
            width: 161px;
            height: 30px;
            margin-left: 12px;
        }
        
        .social-icons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 24px;
            margin-right: 15px;
        }
        
        .social-icon {
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
        }
        
        .content-wrapper {
            width: 725px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 0 48px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin-bottom: 20px; 
            height: 350px; 
        }
        
        .content {
            color: #333333;
            font-weight: 400;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            padding: 24px 0 40px;
            white-space: pre-line;
        }
        
        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 0 0 24px 0;
            line-height:1;
        }
        
        .greeting {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-top:-20px;
            font-weight: 400;
             color: #384860;
        }
        
        .message {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-top:-40px;
            color:#5E5E5E;
        }
       
        .signature {
            margin-top: -90px;
            line-height: 1;
        }
        
        .footer {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666666;
            padding: 40px 48px 24px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eeeeee;
            line-height: 1.5;
            background-color: #ECF8EE;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            margin-top: 40px; /* Added space above footer */
            height: 135px;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            margin: 4px 0;
        }
        
        a {
            color: #0066cc;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        .footer-content {
            max-width: 100%;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
     
        .fcontent1 {
            font-size: 14px;
            transform: translateX(20px);
        }
        
        .button {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background-color: #0A96CC;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 8px 45px;
            width: 179px;
            height: 42px;
            transform: translateY(-50px);
            
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: #007bb8;
        }
        
        .fcontent2 {
            transform: translateX(20px);
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            padding-top: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .fcontent3 {
            transform: translateX(20px);
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-top: 0;
            padding-top: 0;
        }
        .ID {
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #5E5E5E;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-top: -20px;
            display: block;
            font-style: bold;
        }

        .cheers {
            font-weight: 400;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #5E5E5E;
            display: block;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="assets/Zoracom.png" alt="Zoracom Logo" class="zoracom-logo">
            <div class="social-icons">
                <a href="#"><img src="assets/Social icon - Twitter.svg" alt="Twitter" class="social-icon"></a>
                <a href="#"><img src="assets/Vector.svg" alt="Facebook" class="social-icon"></a>
                <a href="#"><img src="assets/Group (2).svg" alt="Instagram" class="social-icon"></a>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content-wrapper">
            <div class="content">
                <h1>{{name}} Declined Their Offer</h1>
                
                <p class="greeting">Hello <span class="subject">Admin</span>,</p>
                
                <p class="message"><span class="Name">{{name}}</span> has declined the offer to join Zoracom. You may archive their record
                     or reach out for clarification.</p>
                 
                <div class="signature">
                    <span class="cheers">Cheers,</span><br>
                    <span class="ID">The HR Team</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <div class="footer-content">
                <p class="fcontent1">
                    Questions or faq? Contact us at <a href="hrteam@zoracom.com">hrteam@zoracom.com</a>. If you'd rather not receive<br>
                    this kind of email. Don't want any more emails from Zoracom? <a href="#">Unsubscribe</a>.
                </p>
                <p class="fcontent2">NSOC Building: 25 Bafaj Crescent, Ogunfayo Lekki-Epe Expressway, Lagos, Nigeria</p>
                <p class="fcontent3">Copyright 2024 Â© Zora Communications Limited. All Rights Reserved.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>